trans-unit.source: Represents a date selection range in a month calendar control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et datoområde for valg i en måned kalender-kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The SelectionRange is the date or dates selected and highlighted on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar> control.
trans-unit.target: SelectionRange er datoen eller datoer er valgt og uthevet på den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar>

trans-unit.source: If only one date is selected, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A> property values will be equal.
trans-unit.target: Hvis bare én dato er merket, den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A>egenskapsverdier vil være likt.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A>

trans-unit.source: The SelectionRange can be changed by the user clicking a date while dragging the mouse pointer across the desired dates, or you can set the range in code.
trans-unit.target: SelectionRange kan endres ved at brukeren klikker en dato ved flytting musepekeren på tvers av ønsket datoer, eller du kan angi området i koden.

trans-unit.source: For example, you might want to have the user enter a date range into two <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox> controls or two <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateTimePicker> controls and set the SelectionRange based on those dates.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel få brukeren til å angi et datoområde i to <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox>Kontroller eller to <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateTimePicker>Kontroller og sett SelectionRange basert på disse datoene.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateTimePicker> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox>
